* Download following software and extract to directory
  ** Directory tree under project
     |--package/
     |  |--busybox/
     |  |    http://www.busybox.net/downloads/busybox-1.22.1.tar.bz2
     |  |
     |  |--linux/
     |  |    https://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v3.x/linux-3.15.1.tar.xz
     |  |
     |  |--u-boot/
     |       ftp://ftp.denx.de/pub/u-boot/u-boot-2014.04.tar.bz2
     |
     |--tool/
        |--toolchain/  
             Sourcery CodeBench Lite for Arm GNU/Linux Release
             http://www.mentor.com/embedded-software/sourcery-tools/sourcery-codebench/editions/lite-edition/

* Build project for qemu simulator
    ./configure --board=qemu
    make uboot_config linux_config busybox_config 
    make initramfs
    make rootfs
   ./sim.sh

* Build project for beagleboard
    ./configure --board=bb
    make uboot_config linux_config busybox_config 
    make initramfs
